                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>February 22<hi rend=\"sup\">nd</hi> 5615</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I beg to acknowledge<lb/> the receipt of your favor conveying\n                the<lb/> resolution of the “Board of Managers” of<lb/> the Congregation over which\n                you so<lb/> ably preside, in which I am honored<lb/> with the appointment “to\n                perform the<lb/> Marriage Ceremony” for my Respected<lb/> friend and colleague the\n                    <persName>Revd I Morais</persName><lb/> I need not say how much pleasure<lb/> it\n                affords me to accept of this honor<lb/> and how sincere my wishes are for the<lb/>\n                happiness of the Bride and Bridegroom<lb/> not only, but also for the continued<lb/>\n                prosperity of your congregation, over<lb/> which, this important step on the<lb/>\n                part of their worthy <add>חזן</add> can not fail<lb/> to exercise a most beneficial\n                result.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3jw8773f/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
